<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #2c2c2c;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #7289da;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(114, 137, 218, 0.2);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #7289da;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #7289da;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .message {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #cccccc;
        }
        .verify-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #7289da, #5b6eae);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .verify-button:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #5b6eae, #4c5c9e);
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #404040;
            color: #888888;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .game-icons {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .expiry-notice {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888888;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">🎮 GameHaven</div>
            <div class="game-icons">🎮 🎲 🏆 🎯</div>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="title">Welcome to the Game, {{ user.username }}!</h1>
        
        <div class="message">
            <p>Your quest to join the GameHaven community is almost complete! Just one more achievement to unlock:</p>
            
            <p>Click the button below to verify your email and gain full access to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>🎮 Game discussions and reviews</li>
                <li>🤝 Trading with other players</li>
                <li>💬 Real-time chat with gamers</li>
                <li>🏆 Special community events</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{ signedUrl }}" class="verify-button">
                🎯 Verify Email & Join the Game
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="expiry-notice">
            This verification link will expire in {{ expiresAtMessageKey|trans(expiresAtMessageData, 'VerifyEmailBundle') }}.
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email was sent from GameHaven. If you didn't create an account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
            <p>Game On! 🎮</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
